    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You grip your claymore tightly and wind it behind your back, preparing to deliver a strike that will wipe away all in front of you. Make a melee Taijutsu attack against a creature within range and all creatures of your choice adjacent to them. You make a separate attack for each creature, dealing your weapon's damage + 2d10. On a hit, a creature must make a Strength saving throw or be knocked Prone.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the damage by 1d10. If this jutsu is cast at B-Rank or higher, a creature who fails the saving throw inflicted by this jutsu is also Dazed.</p>",
